{"tid":722131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸專家：國家足球水平低, 因人民生活水平提高","createTime":"2018-06-29T08:30:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T02:52:50.000Z","uid":134071,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"44feccb1411b3f6ca833ae2fb040790f044b0952","tid":722131,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T08:30:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180629/58377150\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180629%2F58377150&d=Zp%2FOZbqkgEy4%2Bn%2FMoifyyC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=c0d8b033\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180629%2F58377150&h=f2eb136d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180629/58377150</a><br />\n<br />\n國足水平低無緣世盃 內地專家：因人民生活水平提高<br />\n<br />\n17,947<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0629 07:59<br />\n<br />\n四年一度的世界盃，再次未見世界人口最多的中國打入決賽周，中國人民大學法學博士、國際關係專家儲殷對此情況進行分析，認為中國國家隊足球水平低，證明了人民的生活水平提高。<br />\n<br />\n儲殷表示：「在中國現時踢足球的都是富人的孩子，現時中國的足球訓練班十分昂貴，窮家孩子無法踢球，沒有場地、沒有草地，而富人的孩子花錢踢球不會持續下去，所以中國足球後繼無人是很正常的事。」儲殷解釋指，如巴西大部份球星，都是在街頭踢球的窮家孩子，像卡卡這樣的富家弟子踢成名堂少之又少。<br />\n<br />\n有內地網民贊同這名「專家」的意見，稱現時人民生活水平提高，很多孩子已不會到球場上踢球。但亦有網民反駁稱，法國、英格蘭等歐洲球隊在世盃表現出色，而且人材輩出，難道這就說明英法兩國生活水平低，所以足球水平才會提升？更有人炮轟儲殷刻意為國足水平低而開脫，不願正視國家隊的各種問題。"},{"pid":"cbd6bf2a5f61f2ea90287391923369ef906204f1","tid":722131,"uid":192004,"like":8,"dislike":9,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T08:30:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3da6a231f5a646137899dc75e1626055dd1959a1","tid":722131,"uid":66686,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T08:32:12.000Z","msg":"咁奧運？"},{"pid":"9869dcd0124bab5aabf746b1ec90d042038bc680","tid":722131,"uid":71237,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T08:32:42.000Z","msg":"以前窮嗰陣又唔見你踢波勁"},{"pid":"a8fc4fd6d7a1a0b26c86f61659ce11a417774ba4","tid":722131,"uid":52946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T08:37:47.000Z","msg":"難怪中國拿金牌咁成功啦 又係多窮人關系"},{"pid":"bc20a8043ffbb66c001b4414a29929160039c4d9","tid":722131,"uid":181318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T08:40:15.000Z","msg":"r撚晒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2287c76dd44b75c37f1da1fb7270a7cc80113e2","tid":722131,"uid":110656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T08:41:44.000Z","msg":"厲害了我的黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5736dde704d39e2bc4330b4a89651673244234c","tid":722131,"uid":157841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T10:40:49.000Z","msg":"又赢一仗"},{"pid":"ce1bc52db22b5f1f177a5a7835771a3caafec5a2","tid":722131,"uid":66202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T10:44:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">贏！</span></span>"},{"pid":"fc8aeb4b874a726e73cf486d0f4f776d7a26f92e","tid":722131,"uid":112618,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T13:27:03.000Z","msg":"乜撚野logic"},{"pid":"259054fcff796e897b964d67b378f0c933b72452","tid":722131,"uid":137704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T13:48:58.000Z","msg":"咁足球夢係爭取降低人民生活水平<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ad0f6fab7dec1f6bcd6bdcf3da036ef87526d1","tid":722131,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T14:24:17.000Z","msg":"真係唔識架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0597e38e9213804083a547cf94810c4fa567c28d","tid":722131,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2